{"article_id":"lfyIpyfGeXNMzZsA","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Trump keeps stiff upper lip","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"as U.S. report details Russia hacking","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"The president-elect insists","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"the cyberattacks had ' absolutely no effect on the outcome of the election . '","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"U.S. intelligence officials on Friday laid out a stark case","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"- both publicly and privately in Trump Tower to the president-elect -","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"that Russian President Vladimir Putin directed a massive cyberattack","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"to \" undermine public faith \" in the democratic process","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"and to \" harm \" Hillary Clinton ' s chances","depth":11},{"id":9,"text":"of beating Donald Trump .","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"It was a high-stakes day","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"in which Trump met face-to-face with top U.S. intelligence officials","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"whom he ' s spent months mocking for their assessment","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"that Russia directed cyberattacks on Democratic targets","depth":12},{"id":14,"text":"to help tip the election in Trump ' s favor","depth":12},{"id":15,"text":"- a conclusion","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"that threatens to undermine Trump ' s victory .","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"Now that the intelligence community has made its assessment official ,","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"sharing the details of their report with President Barack Obama , Trump and the public ,","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"Trump is maintaining a defiant posture ,","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"asserting","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"that officials did not conclude","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"the hacks swayed the election his way .","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"\" While Russia , China , other countries , outside groups and people are consistently trying to break through the cyber infrastructure of our governmental institutions , businesses and organizations","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"including the Democrat National Committee ,","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"there was absolutely no effect on the outcome of the election","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"including the fact","depth":12},{"id":27,"text":"that there was no tampering whatsoever with voting machines , \"","depth":12},{"id":28,"text":"Trump said in his statement","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"after meeting with intelligence officials .","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"The declassified report from the CIA , FBI and NSA , however , didn ' t even weigh in on the issue .","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"\" We did not make an assessment of the impact","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"that Russian activities had on the outcome of the 2016 election , \"","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"the report stated .","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"The clear dispute adds more fuel to the simmering feud between U.S. intelligence officials and the president elect less than two weeks before Inauguration Day , an unprecedented clash","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"pitting national security up against Trump ' s own insecurities .","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"\" It ' s really remarkable to have someone","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"who ' s never been a consumer of intelligence products ,","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"who has no idea about the cycle","depth":13},{"id":39,"text":"of gathering intelligence ,","depth":13},{"id":40,"text":"trying to claim with credibility","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"he knows what ' s going on .","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"He doesn ' t , \"","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"said Thomas Sanderson , the director of the transnational threats project at the Center for Strategic and International Studies in Washington .","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"\" It suggests ...","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"he simply doesn ' t want to agree with the finding","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"that Russia was behind this","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"because it delegitimizes his campaign win . \"","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"Trump ' s stiff statement came","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"after the president-elect and his allies spent much of the day front-running the meeting and the report ,","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"downplaying Trump ' s ties to Russia","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"and calling on lawmakers to investigate leaked details of the report to news outlets .","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"Trump himself Friday morning called all the attention","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"paid to the hacks","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"a \" political witch hunt , \"","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"motivated ,","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"he claimed ,","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"by his political rivals and their sour grapes over his surprising win .","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"\" They got beaten very badly in the election .","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"I won more counties in the election than Ronald Reagan , \"","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"Trump said of his political opponents in an interview with the New York Times .","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"\" They are very embarrassed about it .","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"To some extent , it ' s a witch hunt .","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"They just focus on this . \"","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"Just before 1 p.m. , the full slate of intelligence chiefs arrived at Trump Tower :","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"FBI Director James Comey , CIA Director John Brennan and NSA Director Mike Rogers .","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"While Trump has not called out them by name on Twitter ,","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"he ' s repeatedly disparaged their work ,","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"even claiming","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"that his briefing had been delayed","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"because they needed more time","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"to build their case against Russia .","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"Trump ' s three-paragraph statement on Friday ,","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"issued at 2:34 p.m.","depth":12},{"id":74,"text":"after the meeting wrapped up ,","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"began on a conciliatory note .","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"\" I had a constructive meeting and conversation with the leaders of the Intelligence Community this afternoon .","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"I have tremendous respect for the work and service","depth":13},{"id":78,"text":"done by the men and women of this community to our great nation , ''","depth":13},{"id":79,"text":"Trump said in the opening of the carefully crafted statement","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"which pivoted quickly to the declarative statement at the heart of Trump ' s effort","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"winning the ongoing public relations battle over the legitimacy of the election","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"that he won-after he spent months last fall ,","depth":13},{"id":83,"text":"preparing for a loss ,","depth":13},{"id":84,"text":"asserting","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"that it would be \" rigged . \"","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"After noting","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"that a number of foreign entities try to penetrate U.S. targets ,","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"Trump said","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"that there had been similar attacks against the Republican National Committee","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"but that those attacks failed","depth":13},{"id":91,"text":"because of the RNC ' s \" strong hacking defenses ''","depth":13},{"id":92,"text":"- a topic","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"the intelligence community did not address in Friday ' s report .","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"This was the first time","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"Trump acknowledged the possibility","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"that Russia had hacked several American targets ,","depth":13},{"id":97,"text":"including the DNC ,","depth":13},{"id":98,"text":"something","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"the nation ' s top intelligence officials concluded in October .","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"He said","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"he will appoint a team","depth":13},{"id":102,"text":"upon assuming the presidency","depth":13},{"id":103,"text":"responsible for creating a plan within the first 90 days of his administration","depth":13},{"id":104,"text":"to combat cyberattacks .","depth":13},{"id":105,"text":"Since October , the intelligence community has uniformly stated","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"that Russia was behind those attacks ,","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"but Trump has been unwilling to concede that conclusion ,","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"pointedly casting doubt on the intelligence community at nearly every turn .","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"In a sign of the high tensions","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"surrounding Friday ' s meeting ,","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"both U.S. officials and Trump ' s team attempted to get ahead of the meeting","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"by airing their side of the story .","depth":8},{"id":113,"text":"Both the Washington Post and NBC News spoke to U.S. officials Thursday night ,","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"detailing at least some of the evidence","depth":12},{"id":115,"text":"proving","depth":13},{"id":116,"text":"Russia was behind the cyberattacks .","depth":13},{"id":117,"text":"That the evidence was made public before his briefing","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"provoked Trump to respond on Twitter .","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"\" How did NBC get ' an exclusive look into the top secret report","depth":12},{"id":120,"text":"he","depth":14},{"id":121,"text":"( Obama )","depth":14},{"id":122,"text":"was presented ? '","depth":13},{"id":123,"text":"Who gave them this report and why ?","depth":12},{"id":124,"text":"Politics ! \"","depth":12},{"id":125,"text":"Trump tweeted .","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"He followed that post with one on Friday ,","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"writing","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"that `` I am asking the chairs of the House and Senate committees to investigate top secret intelligence","depth":12},{"id":129,"text":"shared with NBC","depth":12},{"id":130,"text":"prior to me seeing it . ''","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"Trump 's allies on Friday also pushed the idea","depth":9},{"id":132,"text":"that the focus on Russian hacking was part of a larger agenda","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"to discredit Trump 's victory ,","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"and that Trump was simply expressing healthy skepticism about intelligence .","depth":10},{"id":135,"text":"Kellyanne Conway , a senior adviser to Trump , engaged in a contentious interview with CNN ' s Chris Cuomo ,","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"who pressed Conway on whether Trump was \" sheltering \" Russia .","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"\" He ' s not sheltering Russia ,","depth":12},{"id":138,"text":"and don ' t you say that again , \"","depth":12},{"id":139,"text":"Conway shot back .","depth":11},{"id":140,"text":"She also stated emphatically","depth":12},{"id":141,"text":"that `` Russia did n't want Trump to win the election \"","depth":12},{"id":142,"text":"and said ,","depth":12},{"id":143,"text":"`` The idea","depth":14},{"id":144,"text":"that somehow conclusive evidence has been out there in the public domain ...","depth":14},{"id":145,"text":"is simply not true . ''","depth":13},{"id":146,"text":"Instead , she said","depth":12},{"id":147,"text":"that the uptick in attention","depth":14},{"id":148,"text":"paid to the Russian cyberattacks","depth":14},{"id":149,"text":"is a direct result of Trump 's victory and the work of \" those out there","depth":14},{"id":150,"text":"who are trying to delegitimize his presidency ,","depth":15},{"id":151,"text":"review the election results","depth":16},{"id":152,"text":"and you know it. \"","depth":16},{"id":153,"text":"Those","depth":15},{"id":154,"text":"looking to undercut the incoming administration","depth":15},{"id":155,"text":"will fail ,","depth":14},{"id":156,"text":"Conway said ,","depth":13},{"id":157,"text":"simply because of Trump 's decisive victory .","depth":12},{"id":158,"text":"The report","depth":14},{"id":159,"text":"released Friday afternoon","depth":14},{"id":160,"text":"provided sweeping conclusions of Putin ' s direct interest","depth":14},{"id":161,"text":"in tipping the election in Trump ' s favor .","depth":14},{"id":162,"text":"`` We assess","depth":14},{"id":163,"text":"Russian President Vladimir Putin ordered an influence campaign in 2016","depth":15},{"id":164,"text":"aimed at the US presidential election , ''","depth":15},{"id":165,"text":"said the report ,","depth":14},{"id":166,"text":"which is a declassified version of a longer , classified document","depth":15},{"id":167,"text":"the intelligence agencies prepared at Obama 's request .","depth":15},{"id":168,"text":"`` Russia ' s goals were to undermine public faith in the US democratic process ,","depth":13},{"id":169,"text":"denigrate Secretary Clinton ,","depth":14},{"id":170,"text":"and harm her electability and potential presidency , ''","depth":14},{"id":171,"text":"it continued .","depth":12},{"id":172,"text":"The report also said","depth":11},{"id":173,"text":"the Russian government developed `` a clear preference '' for President-elect Donald Trump","depth":13},{"id":174,"text":"as the campaign went on ,","depth":13},{"id":175,"text":"and eventually `` aspired to help President-elect Trump ' s election chances","depth":14},{"id":176,"text":"when possible","depth":14},{"id":177,"text":"by discrediting Secretary Clinton","depth":14},{"id":178,"text":"and publicly contrasting her unfavorably to him . ''","depth":14},{"id":179,"text":"In another sign","depth":12},{"id":180,"text":"of how seriously U.S. officials are taking election-related vulnerabilities ,","depth":12},{"id":181,"text":"the Department of Homeland Security on Friday designated the electoral system as `` critical infrastructure . ''","depth":11},{"id":182,"text":"DHS head Jeh Johnson said","depth":11},{"id":183,"text":"the move would make protecting polling places , election machines , voter databases and other information technology a formal cybersecurity priority for the department .","depth":11},{"id":184,"text":"In the wake of the release of the report on Friday and Trump ' s reaction , House Speaker Paul Ryan distanced himself from the president-elect on Russia ' s alleged tampering ,","depth":9},{"id":185,"text":"saying","depth":11},{"id":186,"text":"Moscow tried to \" meddle . \"","depth":11},{"id":187,"text":"\" Russia has a track record","depth":14},{"id":188,"text":"of working against our interests ,","depth":14},{"id":189,"text":"and they clearly tried to meddle in our political system , \"","depth":13},{"id":190,"text":"Ryan said in a statement .","depth":12},{"id":191,"text":"\" I strongly condemn any outside interference in our elections ,","depth":12},{"id":192,"text":"which we must work to prevent moving forward . \"","depth":12},{"id":193,"text":"Trump has long been criticized for his warm overtures to Putin ,","depth":5},{"id":194,"text":"which has rankled many Russia hawks in Congress .","depth":5},{"id":195,"text":"The president-elect and Putin have continued their praise of each other since Trump ' s surprise win in November ,","depth":5},{"id":196,"text":"and Trump ' s choice of former ExxonMobil CEO Rex Tillerson","depth":7},{"id":197,"text":"- who was awarded Russia ' s Order of Friendship by Putin -","depth":7},{"id":198,"text":"as secretary of state also alarmed those critical of Russia ' s autocratic ruler .","depth":6},{"id":199,"text":"Putin has denied","depth":7},{"id":200,"text":"that Russia directed the hacks of the DNC and the private email account of Podesta ,","depth":8},{"id":201,"text":"which produced embarrassing emails","depth":9},{"id":202,"text":"that proved distracting for Clinton ' s operation .","depth":9},{"id":203,"text":"`` Everyone 's talking about who 's done it .","depth":10},{"id":204,"text":"Does it really matter that much ?","depth":10},{"id":205,"text":"What matters is what 's inside this information , ''","depth":9},{"id":206,"text":"Putin said at an economic forum in Moscow in October .","depth":8},{"id":207,"text":"`` There 's nothing there","depth":10},{"id":208,"text":"benefiting Russia , ''","depth":10},{"id":209,"text":"he added .","depth":9},{"id":210,"text":"`` The hysteria is simply to distract the American people from the contents of what the hackers have posted . ''","depth":8},{"id":211,"text":"Those statements came","depth":6},{"id":212,"text":"shortly after DHS and the Office of the Director of National Intelligence for the first time publicly blamed Russia for the hacks","depth":7},{"id":213,"text":"and concluded","depth":8},{"id":214,"text":"the country was trying to interfere in the U.S. election .","depth":8},{"id":215,"text":"Trump , however , said","depth":6},{"id":216,"text":"he had no reason","depth":7},{"id":217,"text":"to believe that conclusion .","depth":7},{"id":218,"text":"In a December interview with Time magazine ,","depth":10},{"id":219,"text":"when it named him man of the year ,","depth":10},{"id":220,"text":"Trump said","depth":9},{"id":221,"text":"he did not agree with the intelligence community ' s assessment","depth":9},{"id":222,"text":"that Russia was behind the hacked documents","depth":10},{"id":223,"text":"that ended up on WikiLeaks .","depth":10},{"id":224,"text":"\" I don ' t believe it .","depth":9},{"id":225,"text":"I don ' t believe","depth":10},{"id":226,"text":"they interfered , \"","depth":10},{"id":227,"text":"Trump said .","depth":8},{"id":228,"text":"Trump also appeared to side with WikiLeaks founder Julian Assange ,","depth":7},{"id":229,"text":"who told Fox News ' Sean Hannity this week","depth":8},{"id":230,"text":"that Russia wasn ' t the source of the DNC and Podesta emails .","depth":8},{"id":231,"text":"On the eve of Trump ' s intelligence briefing , Clapper and other officials defended their assessment on Russia ' s involvement ,","depth":4},{"id":232,"text":"telling members of the Senate Armed Services Committee","depth":5},{"id":233,"text":"that the intelligence community \" will ascribe a motivation \"","depth":7},{"id":234,"text":"for why Putin would have directed cyberattacks against the U.S.","depth":7},{"id":235,"text":"when it releases its report .","depth":6},{"id":236,"text":"Clapper also said","depth":5},{"id":237,"text":"Trump ' s rhetoric about intelligence agencies is alarming American allies .","depth":5},{"id":238,"text":"`` I 've received many expressions of concern from foreign counterparts about ,","depth":8},{"id":239,"text":"you know ,","depth":9},{"id":240,"text":"the disparagement of the U.S. intelligence community ,","depth":9},{"id":241,"text":"or I should say","depth":8},{"id":242,"text":"what has been interpreted as disparagement of the intelligence community , \"","depth":8},{"id":243,"text":"he said .","depth":6},{"id":244,"text":"He added about Trump :","depth":6},{"id":245,"text":"`` I think","depth":7},{"id":246,"text":"there ' s a difference between skepticism and disparagement . \"","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":493,"left":439,"right":492,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":439,"left":248,"right":438,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":248,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":438,"left":281,"right":437,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":281,"left":249,"right":280,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":249,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":280,"left":278,"right":279,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":278,"left":261,"right":277,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":261,"left":254,"right":260,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":254,"left":250,"right":253,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":250,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":253,"left":6,"right":252,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":252,"left":7,"right":251,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":251,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":260,"left":10,"right":259,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":259,"left":11,"right":258,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":258,"left":256,"right":257,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":256,"left":12,"right":255,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":255,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":257,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":277,"left":273,"right":276,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":273,"left":266,"right":272,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":266,"left":263,"right":265,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":263,"left":262,"right":19,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":262,"left":17,"right":18,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":265,"left":20,"right":264,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":264,"left":21,"right":22,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":272,"left":270,"right":271,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":270,"left":267,"right":269,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":267,"left":23,"right":24,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":269,"left":25,"right":268,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":268,"left":26,"right":27,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":271,"left":28,"right":29,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":276,"left":30,"right":275,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":275,"left":274,"right":33,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":274,"left":31,"right":32,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":279,"left":34,"right":35,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":437,"left":308,"right":436,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":308,"left":296,"right":307,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":296,"left":292,"right":295,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":292,"left":288,"right":291,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":288,"left":287,"right":43,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":287,"left":286,"right":42,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":286,"left":284,"right":285,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":284,"left":36,"right":283,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":283,"left":37,"right":282,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":282,"left":38,"right":39,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":285,"left":40,"right":41,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":291,"left":44,"right":290,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":290,"left":289,"right":47,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":289,"left":45,"right":46,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":295,"left":48,"right":294,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":294,"left":49,"right":293,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":293,"left":50,"right":51,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":307,"left":301,"right":306,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":301,"left":298,"right":300,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":298,"left":297,"right":54,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":297,"left":52,"right":53,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":300,"left":299,"right":57,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":299,"left":55,"right":56,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":306,"left":303,"right":305,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":303,"left":58,"right":302,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":302,"left":59,"right":60,"relation":"attr